# Test CLI functionality
uv run beatstoch generate-bpm 120 --bars 2
```

### Building Documentation
```bash
# Install MkDocs
pip install mkdocs mkdocs-material

# Preview locally
mkdocs serve

# Deploy to GitHub Pages
mkdocs gh-deploy
```

